instructions: put the dinner fork on the left side of the table
put the dinner knife on the right side of the table
put the salad fork on the left of the dinner fork
put the salad knife on the right of the dinner knife
put the soup spoon to the right of the salad knife
put the dessert spoon in the top center of table with bow pointing left
move the dessert spoon to the right of the soup spoon with the bowl pointing up
move the dessert spoon above and between dinner fork and the dinner knife with bowl facing left
put the dinner plate between the dinner fork and dinner knife
put the bread plate above both forks
put the butter knife on the bread plate with the blade pointing bottom left
put the wine glass above the soup spoon
put the water glass to the right of the dessert spoon
put the napkin on the dinner plate
